Yahoo Finance Senior Markets Reporter Josh Schafer examines the details in today's Chart of the Day. headline: Uncertainty, lagging Mag 7, rate cut hopes: Market Takeaways

Yahoo Finance senior reporter Alexandra Canal lays out the session's biggest trading themes, including prevalent uncertainty across markets, the lagging Magnificent Seven, and Wall Street's hopes for three interest rate cuts from the Fed this year.
